name: loading-003-skin-oval
css: .#= id #-#= loading.id # svg { animation-name: #= id #-#= loading.id #; animation-duration: 1.2s; animation-iteration-count: infinite; animation-timing-function: linear; margin-top: #= loading.itemHeight / -2 #px; position: relative; top: 50%; width: #= loading.itemWidth #px; height: #= loading.itemHeight #px; enable-background:new 16 -16 38 38; }
@keyframes #= id #-#= loading.id # { from { transform: rotate(0deg); } to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
svg: <svg viewBox='16 -16 38 38'><g id='oval'><g transform='translate(1 1)'><circle class='st0' cx='34' cy='2' r='12'/><path class='st1' d='M46,2c0-6.6-5.4-12-12-12'/></g></g></svg>
